  <!-- EN: aerial deployed mine -->
  <Trap_AerialDeployedMine.label>空布雷(已部署)</Trap_AerialDeployedMine.label>
  <!-- EN: A tiny anti-personnel proximity mine deployed en masse via LGIS missiles and detonates once hostile personnel is detected within blast radius. Due to the ADM's nature of missile deployment, your colonists don't know their exact location thus won't automatically avoid them! Its small size prohibits complicated IFF system to be installed, rendering it impossible to deconstruct it safely, requiring manual detonation via gunfire or EMP blast to defuse. Its proximity sensor may be accidently triggered by colonists. -->
  <Trap_AerialDeployedMine.description>一枚由LGIS导弹大规模部署小型近炸地雷，一旦在爆炸半径内发现敌对人员就会引爆。由于ADM的性质，您的殖民者可能会无法发现，因此不会像陷阱一样避开他们！它的体积很小，无法安装复杂的敌我识别系统，因此无法安全地对其进行分解，需要通过炮火或EMP爆炸进行手动引爆才能摧毁。它的接近传感器可能被殖民者意外触发。</Trap_AerialDeployedMine.description>
  
